com.sun.identity.xacml.context.impl

Class EnvironmentImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.xacml.context.impl.EnvironmentImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Environment

    public class EnvironmentImpl
extends Object
implements Environment
    The Environment element specifies information about the environment requested in the Request context by listing a sequence of Attribute elements associated with the environment. 

     <xs:element name="Environment" type="xacml-context:EnvironmentType"/>
 <xs:complexType name="EnvironmentType">
    <xs:sequence>
       <xs:element ref="xacml-context:Attribute" minOccurs="0"
       maxOccurs="unbounded"/>
    <xs:sequence>
 <xs:complexType>
